OL,3,CDrink and drug driving spot checks to
OL,4,Ctake place during Euros
OL,6,FAs the Euro 2024 tournament begins,
OL,7,Fpolice officers are warning football
OL,8,Ffans that random drink drive checks
OL,9,Fwill be taking place throughout the
OL,10,Fcompetition.
OL,12,FDurham Police are urging people to
OL,13,Fplan ahead for their journey home if
OL,14,Fthey are heading out to watch the
OL,15,Ffootball with a few drinks.
OL,17,FEngland take on Serbia in their first
OL,18,Fgame of the tournament on Sunday 16
OL,19,FJune.
